rows.label: tev910301_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910301_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask about his life on Earth.

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0030
rows.name:
Before I got picked for the White Whale's
crew, I was surveying new species of
plants in the jungles of South America.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0040
rows.name:
Now it's my responsibility to clarify—in
a hurry—the effects that our new home's
flora might have on humanity's future.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0050
rows.name:
And yeah, I have military training. I might
come from academia, but I'll be damned if
I don't pull my own weight around here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_JNK0060
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910301_SEL0070
rows.name: Ask about the plants on Mira.

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0080
rows.name:
Most of Miran flora is still unidentified,
but as a rule of thumb, be extremely careful
when encountering a new specimen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0090
rows.name:
Once you've picked up enough samples
to analyze, I would recommend clearing
out quickly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0100
rows.name:
This place is just as dangerous as the
Amazon—most likely moreso. You should
really proceed under that assumption.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_JNK0110
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910301_SEL0120
rows.name: Ask what's happened to Ted.

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0130
rows.name:
You know, my subordinates have been
voicing their support for Ted's endeavor,
and in no small number at that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0140
rows.name:
What he did must've inspired them,
because they've been working with
a lot more enthusiasm than normal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0150
rows.name:
This whole affair has gone to show me—
never underestimate the passion of youth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_JNK0160
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910301_SEL0170
rows.name: Ask about the genetic data you gathered.

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0180
rows.name:
From a global perspective, the data you
and Ted collected is just a small fragment
of the whole picture.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0190
rows.name:
Then again, we didn't exactly have the
most complete genetic database back on
Earth, either. But we still keep on trucking.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0200
rows.name:
This time, we'll be sure to consciously
preserve a snapshot of this planet. We'll
go bearing proof that Mira once lived.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0210
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910301_MSG0220
rows.name: Cancel
